text: Coles Supermarkets is an Australian supermarket chain owned by Wesfarmers (Coles Group before it was taken over on 23 November 2007). With over 750 stores nationally and more than 60,000 employees, Coles currently has the second-biggest market share behind Woolworths Supermarkets. ==Related pages== *Coles Group *Wesfarmers *Coles Express *Bi-Lo *Liquorland ==References== == Other websites == *Coles Supermarkets *Coles Near Me Category:Supermarkets of Australia Category:1914 establishments Category:1910s establishments in Australia
